   UNIVERSITY-RESIGNATION (San Antonio) _ Sam Kirkpatrick announces
he will resign as president of the troubled University of Texas at
San Antonio, effective in a year. University officials say the
resignation was not forced. By JEANNE RUSSELL.
</P>
<P>
   PRIEST-RESIGNATION (San Francisco) _ The Rev. James Aylward,
pastor of St. Catherine of Siena Catholic Church, announces he is
leaving the church due to ``personal and administrative
pressures.'' He admitted an incident of nighttime wrestling with an
adolescent male rectory worker. By ELIZABETH FERNANDEZ.
</P>
