<HEADLINE>
FOR ECONOMISTS, THE VALUE OF PRESERVATION BEYOND PRICE 
</HEADLINE>
   &HT;    (This is one of five special ``one-shot'' features culled from
NATURAL ORDER, a special news section from The New York Times
