computer, and I'm not having as much fun as you might think. I have
come to dread new computers. Used to be, getting a computer was the
most exciting thing in the world. I was like a kid at Christmas.
Now I'm like Scrooge. It's more work than it's worth. (Warner,
Atlanta Journal-Constitution) MOVED.
